data.name: layOrderList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'INJ' JUNDAL_TABLE ,'%' JUNDAL_PART ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,'O' IN_OUT_GUBUN ,FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, TRUNC(A.ORDER_DATE)) GWA ,A.DOCTOR DOCTOR ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME ,C.RESER_DATE RESER_DATE ,C.SILSI_REMARK COMMENTS ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,C.ACTING_DATE ACT_DATE ,A.PKINJ1001 PKINJ1001 ,FN_DRG_HANGMOG_NAME(C.HANGMOG_CODE) HANGMOG_NAME FROM INJ1001 A , INJ1002 C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND C.FKINJ1001 = A.PKINJ1001 AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '3' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '%' AND '%' = '%')) AND :f_message_gubun = '0' AND C.SILSI_REMARK IS NOT NULL ORDER BY C.ACTING_DATE DESC, C.RESER_DATE DESC, A.ORDER_DATE DESC, C.GROUP_SER, C.MIX_GROUP, C.SEQ

data.name: layActing.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, TRUNC(SYSDATE)) ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, SYSDATE) ,B.ACTING_DATE ,B.HANGMOG_CODE ,FN_DRG_HANGMOG_NAME(B.HANGMOG_CODE) FROM INJ1001 A , INJ1002 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.ACTING_DATE = :f_act_date AND A.PKINJ1001 = B.FKINJ1001 AND :f_message_gubun = '0' ORDER BY 3 DESC

data.name: layOrder.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'INJ' JUNDAL_TABLE ,'%' JUNDAL_PART ,A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,'O' IN_OUT_GUBUN ,FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, TRUNC(A.ORDER_DATE)) GWA ,A.DOCTOR DOCTOR ,FN_BAS_LOAD_DOCTOR_NAME(A.DOCTOR, A.ORDER_DATE) DOCTOR_NAME ,C.RESER_DATE RESER_DATE ,A.JUBSU_DATE JUBSU_DATE ,C.ACTING_DATE ACT_DATE ,A.PKINJ1001 PKINJ1001 ,FN_DRG_HANGMOG_NAME(C.HANGMOG_CODE) HANGMOG_NAME FROM INJ1001 A, INJ1002 C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND C.FKINJ1001 = A.PKINJ1001 AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL ) OR (:f_gubun = '3' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NOT NULL )--AND NVL(B.MESSAGE_GUBUN, 'N') = 'Y') OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND A.ACT_DATE IS NULL) OR (:f_gubun = '%' AND '%' = '%')) AND :f_message_gubun = '0' ORDER BY C.RESER_DATE, A.ORDER_DATE, C.HANGMOG_CODE
